      "Artificial Intelligence (Code 417)": ["Communication Skills-II", "Self-Management Skills-II", "ICT Skills-II", "Entrepreneurial Skills-II", "Green Skills-II", "Introduction to AI", "AI Project Cycle", "Data Science", "Computer Vision", "Natural Language Processing", "Evaluation"],
